@node Main "Numo - Documentation"

                               'Numo' 1.11

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Numo' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you have to find the pairs of numbers
so that one number is corresponding to the other, by following the type of
mathematical operation (addition, subtraction, multiplication or division)
with the Code Number. When you have found all the pairs of corresponding
numbers, the remaining number is the solution of the game.

  Have fun!

